That is correct, but it is available as a book:

      Xuejia Lai, ``On the Design and Security of Block Ciphers'',
      ETH series in Information Processing (Ed. J.L.Massey), Vol.1,
      Hartung-Gorre Verlag, Konstanz, 1992.
      ISBN 3-89191-573-X

It can be obtained (for 68 DM) from:

